articles.title: India Women vs Australia Women 3rd T20I Highlights: Australia Win By 7 Wickets, Clinch Series 2-1 - NDTV Sports
articles.description: India Women vs Australia Women 3rd T20I Highlights: Australia chased down a 148-run target in just 18.4 overs to defeat India by seven wickets, and clinch three-match T20I series 2-1
